ow-applications-for-basic-social-assistance-are-processed" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> How applications for basic social assistance are processed</a></li><li class="has-children " ><a class="has-children " href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;kela&#x2e;fi&#x2f;web&#x2f;en&#x2f;social-assistance-payment" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> Payment</a></li><li ><a href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;kela&#x2e;fi&#x2f;web&#x2f;en&#x2f;bank-statements" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> Bank statements</a></li><li ><a href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;kela&#x2e;fi&#x2f;web&#x2f;en&#x2f;basic-social-assistance-for-bills" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> Basic social assistance for bills</a></li><li class="has-children " ><a class="has-children " href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;kela&#x2e;fi&#x2f;web&#x2f;en&#x2f;social-assistance-report-changes-in-your-circumstances" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> Report changes in your circumstances</a></li><li class="has-children " ><a class="has-children " href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;kela&#x2e;fi&#x2f;web&#x2f;en&#x2f;social-assistance-how-to-appeal" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> How to appeal</a></li><li ><a href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;kela&#x2e;fi&#x2f;web&#x2f;en&#x2f;faq-social-assistance" > <i class="icon-angle-right"></i> Frequently asked questions</a></li></ul>
