	<li class="first breadcrumb-truncate"><a href="https://www.kela.fi/web/en/main-page" >Our Services</a><span class="divider">/</span></li><li><a href="https://www.kela.fi/web/en/social-assistance" >Social assistance</a><span class="divider">/</span></li><li class="current-parent breadcrumb-truncate"><a href="https://www.kela.fi/web/en/social-assistance-in-the-coronavirus-situation" >Social assistance in the coronavirus situation</a><span class="divider">/</span></li><li class="active last breadcrumb-truncate"><a href="https://www.kela.fi/web/en/temporary-compensation-due-to-an-epidemic-outbreak" >Temporary compensation due to an epidemic outbreak</a><span class="divider">/</span></li>
